The other error is quite self-explanatory:
```

  CMAKE_CUDA_ARCHITECTURES must be non-empty if set.
```

set CMAKE_CUDA_ARCHITECTURES to the compacity that your GPU supports. find it at https://developer.nvidia.com/cuda-gpus and search for your GPU. set it correctly. (eg. if compute compacity is 5.2, set CMAKE_CUDA_ARCHITECTURES to 52 by appending flag "--cmake_extra_defines CMAKE_CUDA_ARCHITECTURES=52" in your build commandline)
